  "_comment": [
    "base_character.json — 角色立绘基础工作流",
    "节点 title 与 scripts/utils/workflow_template.py 中的快捷方法对应：",
    "  set_checkpoint  → 'CheckpointLoaderSimple'  widgets_values[0] = ckpt 文件名",
    "  set_lora        → 'LoRA Loader'              widgets_values[1]=lora名 [2]=model_weight [3]=clip_weight",
    "  set_prompts     → 'Positive Prompt' [0] / 'Negative Prompt' [0]",
    "  set_seed        → 'KSampler'                 widgets_values[0] = seed",
    "  set_reference_image → 'Load Reference Image' widgets_values[0] = 图像文件名",
    "拖入 ComfyUI 界面后，先在 Preferences → Enable Node Title Editing 确认各节点 title 正确",
    "工作流数据流：",
    "  CheckpointLoader → LoRA Loader → (model/clip) → KSampler",
    "  CLIPTextEncode(positive) ──────────────────────→ KSampler",
    "  CLIPTextEncode(negative) ──────────────────────→ KSampler",
    "  EmptyLatentImage ──────────────────────────────→ KSampler → VAEDecode → IP-Adapter → SaveImage",
    "  Load Reference Image → IP-Adapter Encoder ─────→ IP-Adapter"
